# MasteryLab Project Context

## Overview
MasteryLab is a premier dance training platform in Zurich, Switzerland, focusing on Bachata, Sensual, and Lady Style.
The website serves as a landing page for labs (workshops), a registration portal for students, and a hub for community updates.

## Tech Stack
- **Frontend**: HTML5, CSS3 (Custom Design), JavaScript (Vanilla)
- **Backend/Database**: Supabase (Auth & Database), Google Sheets (Backup via App Script)
- **Forms**: FormSubmit.co & Google Apps Script
- **Hosting**: GitHub Pages / Static Hosting requiring Clean URLs (no .html extensions)

## Key Files
- `index.html`: Main landing page with Hero section and Lab overviews.
- `style.css`: Core styling (Variables, Reset, Components).
- `script.js`: Main interactivity (Mobile menu, Modals, Form handling).
- `supabase.js`: Auth helper built on Supabase SDK.
- `michael-mayra.html`: Specific event landing page.
- `register.html` / `login.html` / `portal.html`: Auth flows.

## Design System
- **Colors**: Black (#050505), Electric Red (#D6001C), White text.
- **Fonts**: 'Anton' (Headings), 'Outfit' (Body).
- **Vibe**: Electric, Artistic, Premium, High-Energy.

## Protocols
- **Images**: WebP format, lazy loading (except Hero).
- **SEO**: Clean URLs, Semantic HTML, Meta descriptions.
- **Automation**: Google Sheets integration for leads.
